<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan></del> etc das <expan>habe<ex>n</ex></expan> wır wol <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> . Nu <expan>w<ex>er</ex>en</expan> wır <expan>ſöllıch<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
